title: IP2 Project Clip of the Day #1
description: Throughout the year we will upload current clips for our snowboard team while they are on the road filming for new snowboarding video project IP2. The clip may be a hammer our just a little insight to what is going down. Clip #1 is Seth Huot with a creative gap.
